<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="49378">Distribution</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="49378">Holarctic species recorded from a small number of European countries; however, its distribution from Scandinavia to Greece indicates its potential occurrence all over Europe.</paragraph>
